title: Floral Printed Wooden Wall Clock ? 12x16 Inch Decorative (Without Battery)
description:
Add a refreshing touch of nature to your walls with this beautifully crafted Digital Printed Wooden Wall Clock. Measuring 12x16 inches, this rectangular timepiece showcases a delicate floral pattern with soft blue and pink leaves, creating a serene and elegant aesthetic.

Made from durable wood, the clock features bold Arabic numerals and sleek black hands for easy readability. Its battery-free design ensures hassle-free maintenance, while the hook-mounted setup allows for quick and secure installation on any wall.

Whether you're decorating a living room, bedroom, office, or hallway, this floral wall clock brings both function and charm to your interior. It?s a perfect blend of art and utility?ideal for those who appreciate minimalist design with a touch of nature.
